      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TANDANYA (1) has been in the placings at his last two runs, most recently when third (22.68) in a Maiden FIN over 400m at Geelong. Look for sharp improvement here. RAVEN'S CALL (4) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at Geelong over 400m behind Aston Aquitaine (22.94) in a Maiden FIN. Was in the money the start prior. In the mix. DR. NAKITA (6) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 3.5 lengths into third (24.75) at Sale in a Maiden over 435m. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Likely to be in the finish again. BLOWING TRUMPETS (2) is a newcomer from the Jacqueline Berry kennel. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Profiles nicely and can feature in the finish.",
